Bug-fixes:
1. make install works on Solaris. Used to die with symlinks. (Rorik)

Feature changes:
1. Changing attribute values with ncap works as advertised (Henry)

Other user-visible changes:
1. The build procedure assumes DODS v. 3.4+ is installed. (Rorik)
   Building with DODS v. 3.3- is no longer supported.

